    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Land depressions having a more flattish landscape, with less precipitous slopes, than canyons or gorges.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
